            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Sure. You need to change `.infer_type()` for the comprehension nodes in `ExprNodes.py` to infer the type of the appended items. I suggest adding a new test file for this, e.g. `tests/run/comprehension_type_inference.pyx` since it's testing a specific intersection of features and needs a number of tests that cover the different comprehension types and different types of items (different Python types, C numbers, …). Ask here if you need more advice.",
            "created_at": "2026-05-12T18:04:21Z",
